[section#expos.only.types
    [:en] Exposition-only types
    [:zh_CN] 仅用于解释的类型
]

[para]
[:en]
Several types defined in Clauses [#language.support] through [#threads] and
Annex [#depr] that are used as function parameter or return types are defined
for the purpose of exposition only in order to capture their language linkage.
[:zh_CN]
从第 [#language.support] 到第 [#threads] 章和附录 [#depr] 中所定义的一些用作函数
的形参或返回类型的类型，其定义的目的仅用于解释，以便明确它们的语言连接。

[:en]
The declarations of such types are followed by a comment ending in
[=Expos].
[:zh_CN]
这些类型的声明式后面跟着以“[=Expos]”结尾的代码注释。

[enter:example]
[codeblock [!:var some-handler] ]
namespace std {
  extern "C" using some-handler = int(int, void*, double);  // [=Expos]
}
[codeblock:end]
[:en]
The type placeholder [`[*some-handler]] can now be used to specify a function
that takes a callback parameter with C language linkage.
[:zh_CN]
这样，类型占位符[`[*some-handler]]就可以用于指定接受一个具有 C 语言连接的回调
形参的函数。
[exit:example]
